name: Laurel
description: LAUREL Gorgeous and elegant shirt-dress made from an absolutely luxurious eco textile. Laurel has a super soft and heavy drape made from the softest twill, that hangs sensuously over the body. A breeze to wear this dress day or night, it feels exceptionally good on. Flattering scooped neckline is very feminine and contrasts nicely with the militaristic epaulettes and button down front. Curved hemline shows off a little leg, and would look great with a pair of tall boots, or some cute sandals next summer. You'lll be wearing this time and time again. Designed and made in Toronto, Canada. ECO textiles are used in this dress. (lyocell/tencel) 100% lyocell (tencel) Hand wash cold, hang to dry.

name: Plunge
description: PLUNGE This rough yet elegant top billows and folds around a deep plunging neckline, which accentuates the neck and is both bold and sexy. The hem is fitted in the back and V's downward in the front for an avant garde look. The knit fabric has a subtle grey fleck giving a worn in, edgy look. Plunge drapes beautifully over a belt or high waisted skirt, or hangs loose and effortlessly over a pair of jeans. Designed and made in Toronto, Canada. 100%polyester Machine wash cold, cool dryer.

name: Urge
description: URGE Lingerie inspired dress Urge, with it's ultra modern yet old world feeling is nothing less than the fabulous party dress of this holiday season. Classic and flattering lines, yet modern and edgy with it's bra elastic straps, and mix of mesh & leather bodice details. Simple and flattering fit showing off all your fantastic curves. Back has vent and invisible zipper closure, slightly tapered hemline to give that extra elongated look. Designed and made in Toronto, Canada. 54%cotton/ 43%polyester/ 5%spandex Hand wash, hang to dry. / Dry clean.

name: Drift
description: DRIFT Structured, yet draped racer back top with a unique and textural krinkle surface contrasts beautifully with the sleek structured neckline. Quite elegant, yet simple enough to dress up your favorite jeans. Looks great belted over the MODE skirt. Designed and made in Toronto, Canada. 100%polyester body 54%cotton/ 45%polyester/ 5%spandex shoulder piece Machine wash cool, cool dryer.

name: Bold
description: BOLD This mini-capelette with it's vintage yet highly modern styling looks great over a sweater or leather jacket. Dress up your favorite outfit with BOLD thrown over your shoulders. Fastens at the neck with a button closure, lined with a gorgeous twill lining and ribbon hang tab. Elongated epaulettes running all the way down the sides make this piece exceptionally militaristic and sharp. Match this with REGIMENT for a full miliary look. Designed and made in Toronto, Canada. 55%polyester/ 45%wool 52%viscose/ 48%polyester twill lining Dry clean.

name: Exo
description: EXO This ultra soft top flows easily over the body, loose and effortlessly elegant with a raw edged flounce. The chic leather racerback straps give the top a slight edge, while the keyhole detail in the back is quite stunning. Perfect tucked into a skirt, or flowing long over a pair of skinny jeans. Process: The desire to build a look that references vintage men's suspenders, using leather and large buttons. Exo is about the contrasting nature of the rigid and rough leather mixing with the feminine and soft draped knit for an overall soft yet powerful look. Designed and made in Toronto, Canada. ECO textiles are used in this shrug (lyocell/tencel) 100% lyocell (tencel) Leather harness Machine wash cold. hang to dry. Remove leather before washing.

name: Rev
description: REV This posh cowled shrug scoops around the back of the neck and hangs loose and billowed over the bust. It's unique avant garde cut can add a new dimension to any outfit. Rev can be worn with a skirt as a sleek backless top, or over an outifit as an elegant solution to a cool fall breeze. Designed and made in Toronto, Canada. 100% polyester front 62% polyester/ 33%rayon/ 5%spandex back and sleeves Machine wash cold, hang to dry.

name: Embody
description: EMBODY This elegant sweater-knit shrug sweeps up over the back of the neck and surrounds the shoulders. An overlayer of grosgrain ribbon compliments and adds structure to the organic cowled neck. Soft and cozy, Embody is a chic way to cover up on a fall day while complimenting any outfit. Designed and made in Toronto, Canada. ECO textiles are used in this shrug. (lyocell/tencel) 94%acrylic/ 6%spandex sweater knit 100%lyocell (tencel) body overlayer Machine wash cold, hang to dry.

name: Dada
description: DADA This loose fitting, long top make of a soft thin fabric skims gracefully across the body looking effortless and chic. The top features hauntingly beautiful abstract prose extracted from a spam email printed in thick black ink. The perfect top to throw on with a pair of skinny jeans and heels. Designed and made in Toronto, Canada. Individually hand printed locally in the Kensington Market. 80%viscose, 20%linen Hand wash cold, hang to dry.

name: Dual
description: DUAL Dualistic in nature this cropped cardigan jacket can be worn several different ways. For a full on military look it can be fully buttoned up the front, wear it open for a casual look with it's draped neckline or button at the waist for a structured collared look. Easy to throw on over your favourite blouse or printed tee, perfect for those crisp fall days. Designed and made in Toronto, Canada. 62%polyester/ 33%rayon/ 5%spandex Machine wash cool, cool dryer.

name: Rorschach
description: RORSCHACH This loose fitting, long top make of a soft thin fabric skims gracefully across the body looking effortless and chic. The exclusively designed inkblot graphic bleached into the fabric adds an element of originality to the top. The perfect top to throw on with a pair of skinny jeans and heels. Designed and made in Toronto, Canada. Individually hand printed locally in the Kensington Market. 80%viscose, 20%linen Hand wash cold, hang to dry.

name: Ease
description: EASE This oversized sheer shirt breezes over the body, playing off the just-threw-on-your-boyfriend's-shirt aesthetic. A luxurious blend of silk and cotton has a soft tissue like transparency. The utilitarian-chic military inspired epaulettes pull the sleeves into structured folds, and the collarless neckline scoops slightly to show off a feminine neck. This top is gorgeous tucked into a flirty skirt, or belted and long over your favorite dark jeans. Enjoy this piece for years to come it's classic style can be accessorised season after season. Designed and made in Toronto, Canada 60%silk/ 40%cotton Dry clean.

name: Vamp
description: VAMP Minimalist and stylish, Vamp is sharp and bold, great for the design office yet elegant enough to wear for a night out. Match this piece with practically anything in your wardrobe. A staple item with an edge. Wear it dressed up with a skirt or casually with a pair of jeans on the weekend. Designed and made in Toronto, Canada. ECO textiles are used in this top. (lyocell/tencel) 100% lyocell (tencel) Hand wash, hang to dry.

name: Velocity
description: VELOCITY This slouchy, billowy top is comfortable and effortless while still being chic and interesting. The square silver hardware is a striking detail, ruching the front to create elegant folds. The exposed tape running vertically on the front gives Velocity a deconstructed edge. A perfect top to throw over leggings, jeans or wear with a skirt and heels. Designed and made in Toronto, Canada. ECO textiles are used in this top. (lyocell/tencel) 100% lyocell (tencel) Hand wash cold, hang to dry.

name: Caged
description: CAGED This dress is fantastically sexy with it's strapping details and fitted lingerie style bodice. Easy to wear as it's heavy knit skirt fits all a girl's curves. The exposed gunmetal back zip gives it a hard edged appeal. Classic and modern, a definite stand out at an event or party. We know you'll love the way you'll feel wrapped up in this! Designed and made in Toronto, Canada. 52%nylon/ 48%cotton upper area 62%polyester/ 33%rayon/ 5%spandex lower area Machine wash cold, hang to dry.

name: Liberty
description: LIBERTY Mad men inspired dress with ultra modern fit. Absolutely great to accentuate bust lines of any size. Nipped in waist with a contrast of pleather gives that hourglass look. Matched epaulettes on the shoulders are a cute vintage military element. Great for the office or holiday events. Available in: grey & black / black & black. Designed and made in Toronto, Canada. 63%polyester/ 37%wool body 70%polyurethane/ 30%polyester pleather details 52%viscose/ 48%polyester lining Dry clean.

name: Quinn
description: QUINN Quinn's paradox, with that tough-as-nails exterior contrasting with the soft cowl neckline and sleeves. A powerful and tailored look makes it easy to transition from a day at the office to an evening out. The mix of very modern fabrics, both slick and textured make this chic factory/luxe aesthetic come alive. With it's accentuated and fitted underbust styling and exposed gunmetal zip in the bact, it's unmistakably edgy in nature. Designed and made in Toronto, Canada 52%nylon/ 48%cotton lower area 100%polyester upper area Machine wash cold, hang to dry.

name: Strut
description: STRUT Fabulous jacket for an instant look of refinement, avant garde and underground. Sexy and edgy with it's transitional hood/cowled neckline. Angled and draped front give the zipper a sensuous and snakey look. Full on metal hardware mixing with the soft boiled wool make this piece a go to for days on end. Lovely for cool evening walks or to give an edgy look to any outfit. Designed and made in Toronto, Canada. 60%viscose/ 40%wool 52%polyester/ 48%cotton lining Dry clean.

name: Regiment
description: REGIMENT Regiment, a woolen military styled wedge cap is a sharp accessory to dress up any coat this winter. Enjoy the vintage look with pin curls or victory rolls and some red lipstick. The cap has a button detail and a beautiful grosgrain ribbon interior band. Designed and made in Toronto, Canada 55%wool/ 45%polyester Dry clean.

name: Obscura
description: OBSCURA Gorgeous, monochromatic silk scarf to dress up even the darkest of days. A haunting and mysterious design of sumptuous silk make it a go to piece for the cool autumn days. An ease to style this several ways and bring a unique aspect to any outfit. PROCESS: This digital print silk scarf was designed in house after an afternoon of experimenting with ink block prints. After many discoveries and psychological assessments of what was seen, our favourite was choose and scanned. It was then rearranged into a beatuiful layered design, and sent off the the printers. Such an exciting moment when the fabric arrived, is was then stitched up and named it Obscura. Some of our early observations were of horned demons, giraffes, and fairies. What do you see? Designed and made in Toronto, Canada. Printed in India. 100% silk crepe Dry clean.

name: Mode
description: MODE This sleek high waisted skirt is classic elegance mixed with tough detailing. The exposed zipper running down the back of the skirt gives it and industrial edge, and the curved seams flatter the shape of the body and add visual interest. Mode creates a very lengthening look that shows off your curves. Wear this piece season after season it's classic beauty will last on and on. Designed and made in Toronto, Canada. 54%cotton/ 42%polyester/ 5%spandex Machine wash cold, cool dryer.

name: Flirt
description: FLIRT This posh mini, layered with sheer fabric is whimsical, moody and fliratious. the soft, gauzy layer drapes over the legs and falls into a sweet silhouette. This diverse skrit can be dressed up with a chic top and blazer, or worn casually with a cute top. Wide elastic waistband makes it easy to slip in and out of. Match this piece with the EASE top for a full look. Designed and made in Toronto, Canada. ECO textiles are used in this skirt. (lyocell/tencel) 60%silk/ 40%cotton overlayer 100% lyocell (tencel) interior Dry clean.

name: Temp
description: TEMP The ultra fitted pencil skirt has a slightly tapered hip flattering cut. Classical and tailored, yet quite sexy with it's leather and buckle details. Sharply dressed and seriously stylish, you'd be sure to be noticed in this. For the full look pair this with the CINCH companion waistcoat. Available in: grey & black / black & black. Designed and made in Toronto, Canada. 63%polyester/ 37%wool 52%viscose/ 48%polyester lining Dry clean.

name: Cinch
description: CINCH This bold and stunning fitted waistcoat has a button front, and adjustable back buckle. Love this piece on it's own or with it's partner skirt TEMP. Great for elongating your figure and a the look of a cinched in waist. Contrast details in pleather. Available in: grey & black / black & black. Designed and made in Toronto, Canada 63%polyester/ 37%wool 52%viscose/ 48%polyester lining Dry clean.

name: Fuse
description: FUSE Versatile doubleknit skirt has an interesting and adjustable rouched hem and stylish wide elastic waistband. Adjusts from an a-line silhouette to a bustle look. Elastic cord and metal findings add to the overall minimalist feel. Enjoy this piece casually on the weekend or dress it up for comfortable yet stylish workday. Designed and made in Toronto, Canada. 62%polyester/ 33%rayon/ 5%spandex Machine wash cold, cool dryer.
